data.description: THIS IS YOUR NEXT HOUSE! Why wait for a newly constructed home when you can move into this stunning residence that exudes model home vibes? Step into a chef's dream kitchen equipped with a natural gas cooktop, dual ovens, and more. The expansive kitchen island seamlessly flows into the family room, creating a welcoming space for gatherings. You'll also find the dining room nestled in a spacious alcove within this open layout. The primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor and boasts a luxurious super shower. Another bedroom and a full bathroom are also on the ground level for added convenience. The outdoor area has been enhanced with an extended covered lanai, complete with a full dining table and a cozy fire pit. Multiple fans ensure a comfortable outdoor experience, and a combination of wrought iron and ivy covered stone fencing ensures privacy, with no rear neighbors to disrupt your tranquility. This exceptional home is situated in the Waterside community of Winter Garden, offering an array of community amenities, including pool, a fitness center, two playgrounds with one being on John's Lake, dock and a clubhouse. Additionally, the use of natural gas extends to the tankless hot water heater, adding efficiency to this already impressive property. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your dream home!  And that's not all! The community also features a convenient dock for fishing and a beautiful park where you can soak in picturesque views of Lake Avalon, adding to the charm and appeal of this wonderful neighborhood.
